## File 1: ArmEnvironment.cs (line 80)
Current: `public override string ToString() => JsonSerializer.Serialize(this);`
The `ArmEnvironment` struct has `Endpoint` (Uri) and `Audience` (string) properties. Replace `JsonSerializer.Serialize(this)` with manual JSON construction that doesn't use `JsonSerializer`:
